features: Ample quantity: you will receive 12 packs of winter theme car tissues boxes in 4 designs and each of the car tissues box comes with 40 sheets 3-ply tissues, sufficient to meet your daily cleaning needs. You can put them in your car, which will bring you great convenience.

Unique winter theme design: the round box car tissue holders are designed with blue winter theme patterns like snowflakes and snowman, greatly enhancing the winter atmosphere. Also, adopting the cylinder shape, our car tissues boxes will not take up too much space in your car or at home. Practical and delicate are not either-or issues anymore!

Appropriate size: each of the winter theme car tissues cylinder measures about 2.67 x 6.3 inches/6.8 x 16 cm and the tissues inside are 5.11 x 7.08 inches/13 x 18 cm, light weight and easy to carry, ideal for cars, trucks, cup holders and other small spaces to make your car look clean and tidy.
3-ply tissues: the 3-ply thickened facial tissues are thicker and more absorbent than the ordinary ones , soft, smooth, safe and odorless, which will give you a comfortable using experience.

Wide range of applications: these winter theme car tissues cylinders are wonderful and exquisite paper loading tools, which are not only ideal for the car, but also for the coffee shop, office, bedroom, study, travel, cup holder, etc., practical and beautiful. Place them in these places to increase the atmosphere of winter and enjoy a pleasant holiday.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Bring Color and Convenience to Your Car! Designed with the cylinder shape, our car tissues boxes are suitable for most car and truck cup holders so you can keep it within reach at all times. No more searching for tissues while you drive! Besides, printed with exquisite patterns, they are also wonderful decorations for your car!

Product Details Easy Open Tops The pre-cut wide mouth makes it convenient for you to take out the tissue inside. Appropriate Size With proper size, the car tissues boxes are ideal for most cars and anyplace without taking up valuable space. Soft and Strong The large size 3-ply tissues inside are thick and absorbent, which will not fall apart when you use them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars You get what you pay for.
reviews.reviewText: Love the decorative cylinders! However, the tissues inside are smaller & rougher than what I consider normal. Also, after you use so many of the tissues, they fall back into the cylinder. Good price for 12 cylinders, but the quality is lacking.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 11, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Hard to open. Punching in the tab causes the whole lid to fall inside so you struggle trying to pull it up and pull the tissue through. The tissues are extremely small, better for a baby or toddler, not adults.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Pricey for little
reviews.reviewText: On a good note, the design is adorable. But, inside the package several canister bottoms had been dislodged so when I picked it up, the tissues all fell out. I was able to put them back. But seen in picture, many bottoms were loose. And one canister had the top pushed in even though they appeared undamaged in shipping. Probably not worth the money.
